==English==

===Proper noun===
'''Third [[Reich]]'''

# [[Germany]] under the [[Nazi]] regime, beginning in 1933 and ending in 1945. Literally "[[third]] [[empire]]" or "third [[realm]]".

===Usage notes===
''[[Reich]]'' in German does not have all of the same connotations as ''[[empire]]'' does in English, notably it does not imply the existance of a monarchy.

